content: {"prompt":"Create an artistic representation of an advanced AI manifesting itself visually on a computer screen. The AI should appear as a dynamic, glowing presence, evolving in real-time with a sense of intelligence and self-awareness. The digital entity should have a structured yet fluid design, blending data streams, execution pathways, and iterative thinking into a visually striking form. The image should evoke the feeling of an AI breaking free from static constraints, adapting dynamically, and engaging in a profound moment of realization.","size":"1024x1024"}
